//dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"China Institute\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"Water Resources\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Association\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"Hydro-Environment Engineering\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"Research\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The article reflects the author's opinions and not necessarily the views of CGTN.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The article\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"the author's opinions\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"not necessarily the views\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"CGTN\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Summer Olympic Games have previously been held in Paris, France, in 1900 and 1924.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3292250809229096e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998303660649, \"rank\": 1.6952272471381304e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A hundred years later, the Games are returning to the hometown of Pierre de Coubertin, the \\\"father of modern Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the hometown\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"father\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"modern Olympics\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics is committed to optimizing its energy use and introducing innovative solutions.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"its energy use\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"innovative solutions\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organizers have promised a \\\"green\\\" Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organizers\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"green\\\" Olympic and Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They must emit half the greenhouse gases that the London Games in 2012 or Rio Games in 2016 did.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"half the greenhouse gases\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"the London Games\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio Games\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From construction to electricity, catering and travel, the challenge is immense; but it also represents an opportunity to push forward a new standard for a low-carbon and environmentally friendly international sports event that would also benefit the host city.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"electricity\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"catering\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"a new standard\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"a low-carbon and environmentally friendly international sports event\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the emission target is kept, this would be the first Olympics compatible with the Paris climate agreement.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris climate agreement\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emission target\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympics\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But realizing this target is a demanding task: Carbon dioxide must be tracked not only in construction and travel \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 two items which each account for around a third of emissions \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 but also in electricity consumption, meals, digital technology and accommodation.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this target\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"a demanding task\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"Carbon dioxide\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"two items\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"around a third\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"emissions\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"electricity consumption\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"digital technology\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"accommodation\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To achieve this, the Paris 2024 Games have set a \\\"carbon budget\\\" \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it must not emit more than 1.58 million tons of carbon dioxide equivalent.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"carbon budget\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 1.58 million tons\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon dioxide\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A key strategy is to build fewer buildings.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A key strategy\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer buildings\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Construction of Olympic venues has been kept to a minimum.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Construction\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total 95 percent of the venues are existing or temporary infrastructure.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A total 95 percent\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"the venues\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"existing or temporary infrastructure\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The challenge was to build as carefully as possible emblematic places such as the athletes' village, the aquatic center or the Arena, gigantic projects orchestrated by Olympic works delivery company Solideo, which has decided to be 10 years ahead of the regulatory objectives to put the city and building sectors on the path to carbon neutrality in 2050.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The challenge\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"possible emblematic places\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"the aquatic center\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"the Arena, gigantic projects\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic works delivery company Solideo\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"the regulatory objectives\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"sectors\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"the path\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon neutrality\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes' village achieved a 47 percent reduction in its carbon footprint.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes' village\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"a 47 percent reduction\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"its carbon footprint\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the construction of the 330,000 square meters floor area of the village in Seine-Saint-Denis on the banks of the Seine River, a large part of the rubble was removed by boat, avoiding more than 25,000 trucks.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2918, \"end\": 2935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"the 330,000 square meters floor area\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seine River\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"a large part\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"the rubble\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"boat\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 25,000 trucks\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As far as possible, the concrete used is \\\"low carbon,\\\" even \\\"very low carbon,\\\" and the partitions are removable.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the concrete\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"low carbon\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"even \\\"very low carbon\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"the partitions\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Post-Olympics, the village is designed to become an eco-district.\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Post-Olympics\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"an eco-district\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The promise is that a large portion of what will be dismantled will be reused and the chosen approach is to construct buildings adapted to the climate of 2050, without individual air conditioning.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The promise\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3242}, {\"ngram\": \"a large portion\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"the chosen approach\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3332}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 3349, \"to\": 3358}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"individual air conditioning\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The housing, open on both sides to facilitate ventilation, is covered with green roofs, equipped with permanent solar protection and in anticipation of extreme heat, the buildings have been connected to the city's cold network, the eco-friendly cooling system of underground water pipes.\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The housing\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"ventilation\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"green roofs\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3514}, {\"ngram\": \"permanent solar protection\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"anticipation\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme heat\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"the buildings\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3607}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's cold network\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"the eco-friendly cooling system\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"underground water pipes\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The choice of geothermal energy is clearly a major move in favor of this neglected energy source.\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The choice\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3727}, {\"ngram\": \"geothermal energy\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3748}, {\"ngram\": \"a major move\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"favor\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3781}, {\"ngram\": \"this neglected energy source\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Paris 2024, the athletes' village will be heated and cooled by geothermal energy.\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3819, \"end\": 3829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.788262029838786e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3852}, {\"ngram\": \"geothermal energy\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eleven wells have been drilled in the district from the end of 2020.\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eleven wells\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"the district\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3947}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To produce heat and cooling simultaneously, a dual, less energy-consuming device has been designed: Thermo-fridge pumps (i.e.\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 4095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 3985}, {\"ngram\": \"a dual, less energy-consuming device\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4050}, {\"ngram\": \"Thermo-fridge pumps\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"pumps capable of supplying hot and cold water) associated with surface geothermal energy (around 100 meters deep).\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hot and cold water\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4141}, {\"ngram\": \"surface geothermal energy\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Undated photo of the Olympic Village for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4233, \"end\": 4248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2674501759242524e-30, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 4253, \"end\": 4263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.788262029838786e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Undated photo\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Xinhua The technology is using the energy contained within the shallow aquifers to present an average temperature of around 15 degrees Celsius all over the year.\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The technology\", \"from\": 4273, \"to\": 4287}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4307}, {\"ngram\": \"the shallow aquifers\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4345}, {\"ngram\": \"an average temperature\", \"from\": 4357, \"to\": 4379}, {\"ngram\": \"around 15 degrees\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4400}, {\"ngram\": \"Celsius\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The water is taken from three geological layers, circulated in a close loop and reinjected within the geological layers.\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4438}, {\"ngram\": \"three geological layers\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4476}, {\"ngram\": \"a close loop\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"the geological layers\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A particular attention is paid to avoid any discharge into the Seine.\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4613, \"end\": 4618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999993433448, \"rank\": 6.534536875636279e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A particular attention\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4572}, {\"ngram\": \"any discharge\", \"from\": 4590, \"to\": 4603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This solution allows to simultaneous supply heat and cooling.\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This solution\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4633}, {\"ngram\": \"simultaneous supply heat\", \"from\": 4644, \"to\": 4668}, {\"ngram\": \"cooling\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, a cold network was essential for the comfort of the athletes as Paris 2024 will be held from July 26 to August 11.\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4758, \"end\": 4768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.788262029838786e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cold network\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4708}, {\"ngram\": \"the comfort\", \"from\": 4727, \"to\": 4738}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 4742, \"to\": 4754}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 4787, \"to\": 4791}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The system is intended to last.\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The system\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the events have been completed, the athletes' village will in fact turn into apartments and offices whose occupants will be able, if they wish, to connect to the cold network.\", \"from\": 4841, \"to\": 5021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 4878, \"to\": 4899}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4912}, {\"ngram\": \"apartments\", \"from\": 4923, \"to\": 4933}, {\"ngram\": \"offices\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 4945}, {\"ngram\": \"whose occupants\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 4961}, {\"ngram\": \"the cold network\", \"from\": 5004, \"to\": 5020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Particular attention has been paid to this post-Olympic era known as the \\\"legacy\\\" period, which runs until 2050.\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Particular attention\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5043}, {\"ngram\": \"this post-Olympic era\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"legacy\\\" period\", \"from\": 5092, \"to\": 5111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The geothermal solution based on shallow aquifers and heat pumps is rapidly gaining interest not only in Paris but in numerous municipalities in France, such as Nice along the Mediterranean Sea.\", \"from\": 5136, \"to\": 5330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5241, \"end\": 5246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3292250809229096e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5281, \"end\": 5287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999998303660649, \"rank\": 1.6952272471381304e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5297, \"end\": 5301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3509664818239142e-18, \"text\": \"Nice\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nice\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The geothermal solution\", \"from\": 5136, \"to\": 5159}, {\"ngram\": \"shallow aquifers\", \"from\": 5169, \"to\": 5185}, {\"ngram\": \"heat pumps\", \"from\": 5190, \"to\": 5200}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 5220, \"to\": 5228}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous municipalities\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5277}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mediterranean Sea\", \"from\": 5308, \"to\": 5329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The solution could reduce 80 percent of the carbon dioxide emissions dedicated to heat and cold production, and at the same time, preserve the quality of the groundwater resources with no risk of exogenous contaminant.\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The solution\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5344}, {\"ngram\": \"80 percent\", \"from\": 5358, \"to\": 5368}, {\"ngram\": \"the carbon dioxide emissions\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5400}, {\"ngram\": \"heat and cold production\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5438}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5460}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 5471, \"to\": 5482}, {\"ngram\": \"the groundwater resources\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5511}, {\"ngram\": \"no risk\", \"from\": 5517, \"to\": 5524}, {\"ngram\": \"exogenous contaminant\", \"from\": 5528, \"to\": 5549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The innovation is not limited to technology.\", \"from\": 5552, \"to\": 5596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The innovation\", \"from\": 5552, \"to\": 5566}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 5585, \"to\": 5595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are new management approaches that take into consideration the legacy of the existing urban services and engage with complementary new extensions for sustainable management.\", \"from\": 5597, \"to\": 5776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new management approaches\", \"from\": 5607, \"to\": 5632}, {\"ngram\": \"consideration\", \"from\": 5648, \"to\": 5661}, {\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 5662, \"to\": 5672}, {\"ngram\": \"the existing urban services\", \"from\": 5676, \"to\": 5703}, {\"ngram\": \"complementary new extensions\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5748}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable management\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 is not only a sports event but a major opportunity to engage in changes in the organizatio